Version: 0.7.8
Date: 9/8/02

For a complete change log, see the development log at:
	http://ilohamail.org/main.php?page=DevLog


NOTES
=====
This version includes performance enhancements in the POP3 library, custom SMTP
support, persistent database connections, and 5 new languages (Chinese, 
Italian, Polish, Brazilian Portuguese, and Swedish).  This version also 
includes numerous bug fixes.


